WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:02.580
Biz sizga dastlabki ikki bosqichni 
qanday bajarishni ko‘rsatdik.

00:00:02.580 --> 00:00:05.020
Agar siz hali ham bu borada 
yordamga muhtoj bo‘lsangiz, 

00:00:05.020 --> 00:00:07.100
bu muammo emas, shunchaki oldingi 
videoni yana ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

00:00:08.270 --> 00:00:11.080
Endi men decrement metodida o‘zgaruvchilarni 
yangilash kerakligini ko‘rsataman.

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.150
Sizdan o‘zgaruvchan miqdorni 
1 dan boshlashni va uni 1 stakan 

00:00:14.150 --> 00:00:16.760
kofegacha yangilashingizni so‘raymiz.

00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:19.360
Men MainActivity.java faylida 
 decrement metodida 

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:20.780
kodni o‘zgartirmoqchiman.

00:00:20.780 --> 00:00:24.110
Biz miqdor o‘zgaruvchisini yaratamiz 
va uni 2 dan boshlaymiz.

00:00:24.110 --> 00:00:27.500
Keyin men o‘zgaruvchilar 
miqdorini 1 ga tenglashtiradigan 

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:28.630
yana bir kod qatorini qo‘shaman.

00:00:28.630 --> 00:00:31.690
Va nihoyat, yangi qiymatni 
ekranda namoyish qildim.

00:00:31.690 --> 00:00:34.270
Keling, uning ishlashini tekshirish 
uchun ilovani ishga tushiramiz.

00:00:34.270 --> 00:00:36.330
Agar men minus tugmasini bossam,
u 1 ga tushadi.

00:00:36.330 --> 00:00:38.044
Men breakpoint qo‘shib, 
miqdor o‘zgaruvchisi 

00:00:38.044 --> 00:00:42.540
yangilanayotganligini ko‘rsatish uchun 
tuzatuvchini ishga tushirishim mumkin.

00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:45.990
 Debug panelini ochish uchun ushbu 
debug yorlig‘ini bosaman.

00:00:45.990 --> 00:00:49.030
 Breakpoint ni olib tashlash uchun 
minus tugmasini bosib 

00:00:49.030 --> 00:00:52.120
va har bir satrdagi kodga ko‘z yugurtiring.

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:53.850
Mazkur holatda, 
birinchi belgi bajariladi, 

00:00:53.850 --> 00:00:57.620
natijada miqdor o‘zgaruvchisi 2 ga teng, 
keyin u 1 ga o‘zgaradi.

00:00:57.620 --> 00:00:59.650
Va keyin ilovani davom ettirib va 

00:00:59.650 --> 00:01:01.824
1 qiymatga ega bo‘lishi uchun 
yangilash kerak.

00:01:02.970 --> 00:01:04.620
Va u ishlaydi.

00:01:04.620 --> 00:01:07.660
 Integer ni qanday yangilash 
kerakligini tushunib oldik,

00:01:07.660 --> 00:01:11.990
o‘zgaruvchini yangi raqamga o‘zgartiring va 
 debugger da qiymatni tekshiring.

00:01:11.990 --> 00:01:13.130
Ammo bu hali ham cheklangan.

00:01:13.130 --> 00:01:16.070
Aslida, o‘zgaruvchan qiymatni 
belgilashdan tashqari 

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:17.530
o‘zgaruvchini yangilashning 
boshqa usullari ham mavjud.

